<TEXT>
 <PERSON> Barry </PERSON> <PERSON> Schweid </PERSON> has covered <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> diplomacy in the <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> East </LOCATION> since 1973.
