Don </PERSON> <PERSON> Ottavio </PERSON>, but sang the part well, with reined-in warmth. <PERSON> Rolf </PERSON> <PERSON> Langenfass </PERSON>, who created costumes for the Met's current Ring Cycle, designed the sets and costumes. Next season he'll work with <PERSON> Prince </PERSON> on a new production of `` Faust'' at the Met.
