PERSON> Carmen </PERSON> <PERSON> Rocco </PERSON>, who treated survivors and consoled families while rescuers clawed through the rubble, said she recalls events just before the disaster and after the site was cleared. `` In between, there was so much pain and so much tragedy that I really blocked it out,'' she said. `` All I really remember is an incredible thunderstorm, and today we had one of those.'' All that remains at the site a year later is vinyl flooring, the tiles at the entrance and a gaping hole in the downtown business district. <PERSON> Levin </PERSON> faces personal injury lawsuits seeking millions of dollars in damages. The city, <ORGANIZATION> Public </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Utilities </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Board </ORGANIZATION> and various construction firms and suppliers have been named as defendants, too. Among the survivors was 32-year-old Mexican <PERSON> Jose </PERSON> <PERSON> Luis </PERSON> <PERSON> Gaytan </PERSON> who suffered brain damage while trapped in the rubble and no longer is able to teach school, said <PERSON> Ernesto </PERSON> <PERSON> Gamez </PERSON>, his attorney. No official report has been released to explain what caused the three-story structure to collapse in a storm that dumped two inches of rain on the city in 30 minutes. The store was built in 1969 and the third floor added in 1975. Dr. <PERSON> Lorenzo </PERSON> <PERSON> Pelly </PERSON>, who hitchhiked to the scene from <ORGANIZATION> Brownsville </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Medical </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Center </ORGANIZATION>, said: `` The first thing I saw there was a guy who had his face crushed between a parking meter and a car parked there on the street.'' <PERSON> Pelly </PERSON> said the outpouring of volunteers from throughout the lower <LOCATION> Rio </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Grande </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Valley </LOCATION> united the region, but he regrets the bickering among rescuers and the decision to dig instead of looking first for survivors. Survivors were not located until hours later.
