<HEAD>U.S. Official in Angola for Talks on Peace Process</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By TONY SMITH</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>LUANDA, Angola (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
