<HEAD>Judge Approves Ticket Refund Plan Between Eastern, Travel Agents</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Airline Discounts, Bjt</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
